115
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,370
Who should I talk to?

116
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:31,990
What should I say?

117
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:33,430
The police department

118
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:35,970
can't just arrest people for no reason, right?

119
00:06:35,970 --> 00:06:36,970
How do you know

120
