123
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,310
Do you think this is because of me?

124
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,680
No, no, I'm just asking.

125
00:06:58,550 --> 00:07:00,640
I don't think they'd arrest me.

126
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:03,030
Yesterday afternoon,

127
00:07:03,050 --> 00:07:05,520
I even had tea with a Japanese general.

128
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,720
You know a Japanese general?

129
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,070
Not exactly.

130
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,040
It was our first time meeting, introduced by a friend.

131
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,480
We chatted a bit

132
