260
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,930
How did you get involved with them?

261
00:14:37,190 --> 00:14:38,720
It's all my friends' fault.

262
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,320
Your friends?

263
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:41,930
What did they do?

264
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:43,440
They're causing trouble everywhere.

265
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,550
It's outrageous.

266
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,380
Causing trouble everywhere?

267
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,130
Who did they take a fancy to?

268
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,960
They don't go after just any woman.

269
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,000
They went after

270
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,860
a rich Korean merchant woman.

271
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,860
A rich Korean merchant woman?

272
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:57,760
They're out of her league.

273
00:14:57,790 --> 00:15:00,190
