274
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:05,350
I don't know how you three

275
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,110
got involved

276
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:11,550
with that Korean woman.

277
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,270
