00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:16,080
you're taking the blame for someone else.

291
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,750
You can explain to me.

292
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:20,710
Why?

293
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:26,930
Honestly, I'm also wondering

294
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:29,470
why the Tokyo police, knowing full well

295
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,030
that only one Chinese man

296
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:33,000
was involved with that Korean woman,

297
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,330
yet they arrest all his Chinese students.

298
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:38,060
Because at that time,

299
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:40,440
you weren't in uniforms,

300
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:42,000
besides...

301
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:45,360
you were still wearing those silly braids.

302
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,160
They wanted to know who you were,

303
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:50,650
