309
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:17,829
I see.

310
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:20,589
You're free to go now.

311
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:22,829
Yes, sir.

312
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:59,720
Connect me to Duke Ayakura's place.

313
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:03,280
