315
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,480
What are you looking for?

316
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:10,720
Tufang.

317
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:12,040
Tufang!

318
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,520
Are you crazy?

319
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,030
Give me the scissors.

320
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:21,430
Tufang, Tufang, Tufang!

321
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,310
Tufang!

322
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:24,520
Have you made up your mind?

323
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,830
You're different from us.

324
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:26,890
How am I different?

325
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,530
What's the difference?

326
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:29,590
If I take off this uniform,

327
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:31,070
