328
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:31,700
Give it to me.

329
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:32,380
Tufang!

330
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,030
Tufang!

331
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:35,590
Listen to me.

332
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,890
I can cut it, but you can't.

333
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:39,920
You have to think about your own future.

334
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:41,220
It's none of your business!

335
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,150
Give me a reason.

336
00:18:42,170 --> 00:18:42,720
Give me a reason

337
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,070
and I'll cut mine with you, okay?

338
00:18:44,070 --> 00:18:44,870
Let me ask you.

339
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,850
Why did we even come to Tokyo?

340
00:18:46,850 --> 00:18:48,520
It's that Hirata again, right?

341
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,550
He's just a lieutenant!

342
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:51,440
Three years ago, I was a field-grade officer!

343
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,430
Who cares if he talks crap?

344
00:18:52,430 --> 00:18:53,310
If we do, we'll never achieve anythingh.

345
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,550
It's not about him.

346
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,660
I just want to cut my braids!

347
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:57,860
It's very important.

348
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,160
No!

349
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:14,030
Providing services to Qing dynasty nobles

350
