353
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:27,720
Assimilating is to cultivate pawns for the Empire.

354
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:32,640
These students will eventually become

355
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,120
the future military

356
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:37,440
and political elites of Qing Empire.

357
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:41,160
Here,

358
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:44,310
we have to plant Japanese ideals in them,

359
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:48,510
and build loyalty

360
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:52,000
and trust toward Japan

361
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,550
among Qing's future rulers.

362
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,480
This is essential.

363
00:19:57,770 --> 00:19:59,570
You should know that.

364
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:01,550
Yes, sir!

365
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:07,840
This is...

366
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:12,830
the Emperor of Japan's century-long plan

367
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:16,280
and the dream of our Yamato people

368
00:20:16,550 --> 00:20:18,070
for generations.

369
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,310
I hope you can

370
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:24,440
keep our mission deep in your heart.

371
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:25,790
Never

372
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:28,250
let your self-esteem, competitive streak,

373
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:31,070
or emotions cloud your judgment.

374
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:37,480
Reshaping their spirits

375
00:20:39,050 --> 00:20:43,290
is all part of the Empire's big strategy.

376
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:51,400
I will follow your teachings by heart.

377
00:20:58,950 --> 00:20:59,990
Sir Hirata.

378
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:15,400
Did you cut your braids?

379
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,170
I did it yesterday.

380
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:18,790
Why?

381
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:22,380
Let's call it a way to show my resolve.

382
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:26,080
You're already excellent,

383
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:28,550
and now you're even more handsome.

384
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:32,400
You're not feeling pressured, are you?

385
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:35,920
I am under pressure.

386
00:21:36,270 --> 00:21:37,550
Yoshiko has been...

387
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:39,030
Let's not talk about this.

