398
00:22:58,510 --> 00:22:59,440
Miss Shuhong.

399
00:22:59,790 --> 00:23:01,520
The principal wants to see you.

400
00:23:01,660 --> 00:23:02,180
Okay.

401
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:46,680
What is it?

402
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,490
What do you want from me?

403
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:51,250
My friends came all the way here.

404
00:23:56,030 --> 00:23:56,590
Please.

405
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:29,380
Stop.

406
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:36,480
Mr. Wu,

407
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:43,510
