440
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:50,850
Unfortunately, it's only half-finished.

441
00:26:51,190 --> 00:26:53,270
You're a bit too impatient.

442
00:26:57,270 --> 00:26:59,960
Besides making counterfeit money,

443
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:02,000
