444
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:05,070
That depends on what you want to do.

445
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:09,030
If you love art,

446
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:11,470
you can make calligraphy and painting.

447
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:14,310
If you want to dine with politicians,

448
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:15,790
then arrange

449
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:19,550
one of your guys in the cabinet.

450
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,510
If one day, you want

451
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:27,000
to take a stroll through the Chinese Imperial Palace,

452
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,680
the best way is

453
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:31,030
to start investing

454
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:33,200
in a Chinese revolutionist like you.

455
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:44,200
we should sit down and talk properly sometime.

456
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:47,800
But there's one condition for working with me.

457
00:27:48,070 --> 00:27:49,350
My money...

458
00:27:50,810 --> 00:27:53,640
can only be used for the revolution.

459
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:56,140
Yes, sir.

460
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:14,880
How did you fall for that person?

461
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:16,680
That person?

462
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:21,200
Yang Kaizhi is my brother-in-law's cousin.

463
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,310
Really?

464
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,990
That's great.

465
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,680
I'll treat you to a meal.

466
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:34,400
A lot of delicious food!

467
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,510
A Korean feast!

468
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,920
Do you want try it?

469
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:38,720
Of course I do.

470
00:28:39,270 --> 00:28:42,680
Then I'm treating you tonight.

471
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:43,930
Let's go.

472
00:29:05,270 --> 00:29:07,030
Come on, let me help you up.

473
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,040
Is that okay?

474
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:08,790
It's fine.

475
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:10,110
Hurry up.

476
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,140
You're really something.

477
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:58,030
You're a real chemist!

478
00:29:58,090 --> 00:29:58,960
Wrong.

479
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:01,550
