485
00:30:16,790 --> 00:30:19,880
That's why I urgently need money.

486
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:21,510
Those stable chemical materials

487
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,920
on the market

488
00:30:22,940 --> 00:30:23,550
are generally

489
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:25,000
very expensive.

490
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:29,270
They're like fine women.

491
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:34,000
How come you never mentioned

492
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:34,960
Shuhong?

493
00:30:36,350 --> 00:30:37,480
Where is she now?

494
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:40,270
She's in Tokyo, but...

495
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:41,510
That's good.

496
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,680
Have her come talk to me.

497
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,370
I only trust her.

498
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,750
I don't feel safe

499
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,100
