500
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:54,400
No.

501
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:55,640
I don't plan

502
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,030
to drag her into this matter.

503
00:30:57,030 --> 00:30:58,160
It's too dangerous.

504
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,750
Then, why should I

505
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:05,200
invest in your dangerous deal?

506
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,160
Didn't you say

507
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,680
you want to stroll through

508
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:13,340
the Chinese Imperial Palace?

509
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:15,920
Well said.

510
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:20,240
But I don't need bombs.

511
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,260
What I need is the intel

512
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:28,000
on the Russian Army in Manchuria,

513
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:28,550
and...

514
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:31,480
accurate info

515
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:34,240
on the Russian Pacific Fleet

516
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,960
at Port Arthur.

517
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,350
That's not too much to ask.

518
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,510
It's a fair deal.

519
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,970
We both get what we need.

520
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,920
Comrades from all over
are coming to Tokyo to look for me.

521
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,580
They desperately need bombs.

522
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:51,070
How much is it

523
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:52,510
to buy materials and upgrade gear?

524
00:31:52,510 --> 00:31:53,750
Make a list.

525
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:54,920
Then...

526
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:58,070
