527
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:00,480
Between you and me,

528
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:03,750
we won't handle the money...

529
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,350
directly.

530
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:08,820
Wait, Mr. Kanyama.

531
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,030
I...

532
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:12,880
I have another question I'm very curious about.

533
00:32:13,550 --> 00:32:15,350
How did you get involved

534
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,920
in this Russo-Japanese affair?

535
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:17,640
Do you have

536
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:20,030
a relative in the cabinet's military department

537
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:21,350
or something?

538
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:25,030
A word of advice,

539
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:31,510
don't get too nosy.

540
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,830
In Tokyo,

541
00:32:34,270 --> 00:32:36,350
this is top-secret stuff.

542
00:32:37,330 --> 00:32:39,000
If you poke around too much,

543
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:42,440
and the Japanese safety police

544
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,680
will come knocking.

545
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:49,920
Watch yourself, Mr. Wu.

546
00:32:51,790 --> 00:32:52,820
Don't

547
00:32:52,850 --> 00:32:55,170
blow up your own roof.

548
00:33:21,930 --> 00:33:24,170
I waited for you two for two hours.

549
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:25,960
Tell me.

550
00:33:26,270 --> 00:33:27,550
Where did you go?

551
00:33:44,410 --> 00:33:46,170
Hold on! Wait.

552
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,200
Excuse me.

553
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,440
Hello.

554
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,210
Who are you looking for?

555
00:33:52,550 --> 00:33:54,110
I'm looking for Shuhong.

556
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:56,070
What's your relationship to her?

557
00:33:56,070 --> 00:33:58,310
I'm her teacher.

558
00:33:58,920 --> 00:33:59,720
Teacher?

559
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:01,290
Yes, I'm her teacher.

560
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,450
I'm very sorry.

561
00:34:04,470 --> 00:34:06,350
