564
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,960
Why aren't you saying anything?

565
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:26,480
I have nothing to say, Principal.

566
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:30,960
It's not that I'm being too strict,

567
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,469
Miss Shuhong.

568
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:36,030
But I can't keep you here anymore.

569
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:40,550
The safety police came here earlier.

570
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:42,929
For Miss Li,

571
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:46,420
