579
00:35:17,110 --> 00:35:17,810
Principal.

580
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,830
Miss Shuhong, it's settled.

581
00:35:31,830 --> 00:35:33,750
You're expelled tonight.

582
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,510
By the way, that man

583
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:38,570
is waiting for you at the school gate.

584
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:57,600
What's wrong?

585
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,450
I've been expelled.

586
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:02,130
Really?

587
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:06,760
Come here.

588
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:08,670
In my opinion,

589
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:09,920
this is all Yifan's fault.

590
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:10,230
You know?

591
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:12,000
He shouldn't have wasted that money.

592
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,230
If you stick with me, Wu Tianbai,

593
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:14,760
and it's like going to school.

594
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,900
I'm like a walking encyclopedia

595
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,750
that you can read for a lifetime.

596
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,310
You're back on your old job?

597
00:36:32,310 --> 00:36:33,270
To be honest,

598
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:35,320
I just got an investment.

599
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,360
Really?

600
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:40,710
How about we team up

601
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:42,520
and open a husband-and-wife shop together?

602
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:44,030
You're being shameless again.

603
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:45,430
Can we really stay apart?

604
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:46,590
We're inseparable, you know that.

605
00:36:46,590 --> 00:36:48,030
You want me run errands for you.

606
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,760
That's right. I'll handle the wheel.

607
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:50,960
You want me sweet-talk others

608
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:51,530
and put on a smiling face.

609
00:36:51,530 --> 00:36:52,930
I'll make plans.

610
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:53,890
You're all talk.

611
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:54,890
You just run errands.

612
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:56,070
So you want to be the hands-off boss?

613
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:58,270
You're naturally the sidekick anyway.

614
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:04,710
Who are you dealing with this time?

615
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,800
Your former boss, Mr. Kanyama.

616
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:08,150
Mr. Kanyama?

617
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,600
He's a Japanese gang member.

618
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,360
What can we do about that?

619
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:13,960
Shuhong.

620
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,800
If you can't dodge it,

621
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,630
it's just your rotten luck.

622
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:18,310
Hands off!

623
00:37:30,550 --> 00:37:31,480
Where do I sleep?

624
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:33,030
Anywhere.

625
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,280
Anywhere?

626
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,000
As long as you don't sleep on the bombs,

627
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,800
you can sleep anywhere you want.

628
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,710
Why are you staring at me like that?

629
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,440
Am I more dangerous than a bomb?

630
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:49,110
This doesn't look like a place for you to sleep.

631
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,710
You didn't go back

632
00:37:50,710 --> 00:37:52,370
to see the Madam of Bamboo Inn?

633
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:53,710
Why would I go see her?

634
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,720
Do you think I don't know?

635
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,190
What do you know?

636
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:59,310
I've seen through you long ago!

637
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:03,430
You're great in every way, except for this one flaw.

638
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,340
What are you looking at?

639
00:38:04,340 --> 00:38:06,600
I'm not even gonna waste my breath on you.

640
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:09,190
As a man in business,

641
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:11,000
you must have some dignity, right?

642
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,860
How can you have no dignity at all?

643
00:38:17,300 --> 00:38:18,360
Bring the box over.

644
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:37,660
I, Kanyama, am the boss here.

645
00:38:38,130 --> 00:38:39,660
And I was elected

646
00:38:39,690 --> 00:38:42,290
by all the senior members with one vote each.

647
00:38:42,550 --> 00:38:43,280
Yes, sir.

648
00:38:44,110 --> 00:38:46,150
I have to call the shots in Shanghai.

649
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:47,030
Yes, sir.

650
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:50,360
I am the rule.

651
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:50,970
Yes, sir.

652
00:38:52,150 --> 00:38:54,150
When I say take the money, you take it.

653
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:55,920
If I want someone dead,

654
00:38:55,950 --> 00:38:57,620
they die.

655
00:38:58,150 --> 00:38:58,880
Yes, sir.

656
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:00,510
Come in.

657
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:03,280
Boss,

658
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,030
Shuhong is here.

659
00:39:08,710 --> 00:39:10,310
When you go back to Shanghai,

660
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:12,840
just tell them what I said.

661
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:16,190
If you have any reports later,

662
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:18,690
just write it like this.

663
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,990
The view's great, life's sweet,

664
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,910
I'm satisfied with everything.

665
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:24,280
Over.

666
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:25,360
Yes, sir.

667
00:39:27,590 --> 00:39:28,590
You may leave now.

668
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:54,630
Shuhong.

669
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:59,030
Mr. Kanyama.

670
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,030
You're pretty.

671
00:40:02,030 --> 00:40:04,030
You've gotten prettier.

672
00:40:05,190 --> 00:40:06,360
Where have you been?

673
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,230
My brother-in-law

674
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:09,000
insisted that I go to Utako Shimoda's school

675
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,130
to study for a while.

676
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:12,440
Utako Shimoda?

677
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:14,760
She's a noble lady in Tokyo.

678
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,150
Lately,

679
00:40:17,630 --> 00:40:19,960
how's your business at shop, Mr. Kanyama?

680
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:21,840
Not so good.

681
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,440
It's slack.

682
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:28,800
Since you left, even the paintings aren't selling well.

683
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:34,390
Mr. Wu asked me to bring this to you.

684
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,930
Here's the thing, Shuhong.

685
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:41,670
I saw Mr. Wu's place.

686
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:44,320
It's a nice location.

687
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:47,840
There's a bakery downstairs.

688
00:40:49,150 --> 00:40:50,030
I can consider

689
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:52,280
renting that shop.

690
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:54,590
Will they agree?

691
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:57,320
The bakery downstairs is doing well.

692
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:59,510
I'll make them agree.

693
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:03,510
Are you also opening a bakery?

694
00:41:03,510 --> 00:41:04,440
No, no, no.

695
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:06,440
We'll open a stationery store.

696
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:08,160
I want you to handle distribution for me.

697
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:09,160
What do you think?

698
00:41:10,030 --> 00:41:12,320
This way, it's both discreet and convenient,

699
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,030
am I right?

700
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,030
As for the fee,

701
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,590
we can sign

702
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:18,920
an agreement right now.

703
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:22,150
Yes, sir.

704
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:29,000
Right, this is it.

705
00:41:32,830 --> 00:41:35,480
[Agreement]
